Hound will no longer cost energy while shooting. +0.5% Hound's total DMG for each point of current energy. If Hound does not deal damage within 5 seconds, +4 energy points cost per second (up to 20 energy points cost per second). 
At 40 energy, +50% RoF; 
At 80 energy, Hound's total DMG increase to 0.8%; 
At 140 energy, hitting will cause once DMG to an additional enemy within 5m; 
At 200 energy, attacking will cause elemental effect and 50% chance of triggering an Elemental Effect.
